u}\sigma_{
u} =  rac{1}{h
u} \left(  rac{L_0}{4\pi r^{2}} \left( rac{
u}{
u_0}ight)^{-3/2} ight) \left( \sigma_0 \left( rac{
u}{
u_0}ight)^{-3} ight) $$
$$ =  rac{L_0 \sigma_0}{4\pi h r^{2}}  rac{1}{
u} \left( rac{
u}{
u_0}ight)^{-9/2} =  rac{L_0 \sigma_0}{4\pi h r^{2}}  rac{
u_0^{9/2}}{
u^{11/2}} =  rac{L_0 \sigma_0 
u_0^{9/2}}{4\pi h r^{2}} 
u^{-11/2} $$
让我们为这组项定义一个常数，$C_{\Gamma} =  rac{L_0 \sigma_0 
u_0^{9/2}}{4\pi h r^{2}}$。微分光致电离率为 $C_{\Gamma} 
u^{-11/2}$。

每个原子的光致加热率 $H$ 由频率为 $
